{"tid":1237520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議大家向共產黨學習","createTime":"2019-06-17T14:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T14:24:19.000Z","uid":22465,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3f5fd8c90730aa1f717d5221b807868e01bb35","tid":1237520,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"支共最叻對敵人攪分化，而家一哥將隻鑊推晒比下層，係時候學下支共分化前線警犬同高層，建議大家係社交媒禮（FB IG）多發表意見話鄧班前線唔抵，比人用完即棄，激起班警犬仇視高層既心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班毅進仔同佢地家人無乜腦，睇得多呢d就會覺得自己好委屈，慢慢就會屌埋高層一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住，敵人既敵人就係朋友，分化佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好有埋長輩圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6deab4774c1a0b083fe9bdf40b81bacbc4f35d","tid":1237520,"uid":22465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"拉一派打一派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c72e2f79002bb3f04120b1d0dfe76218be5e4a0","tid":1237520,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"要讀毛語錄"},{"pid":"0084756855a15b7ba5ce16e75b3435dd1e138c40","tid":1237520,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c72e2f79002bb3f04120b1d0dfe76218be5e4a0","tid":1237520,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"要讀毛語錄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:56:01.000Z","msg":"將敵人個套化為己用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11744e8811d8c67b6f580ead2458a25a904c52c6","tid":1237520,"uid":252510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"全面進駐FB反智page<br />\n<br />\n撐警察，反局長！"},{"pid":"9aa2b6e761163e124aa11f4e0484b6d8b006fd44","tid":1237520,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T1